== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenroku|ja|天禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[972]] {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kūya|ja|空也|12=draft|12=draft}}, the founder of the {{ill|Odori Nenbutsu|ja|踊念仏|12=draft|12=draft}} tradition (born {{ill|903|de|903|ja|903|zh|903|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1585]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tachibana Michiyuki|ja|立花道雪|12=draft|12=draft}} {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165}}, a {{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1513|de|1513|ja|1513|zh|1513|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1603]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Takeda Nobuyoshi|ja|武田信吉|12=draft|12=draft}}, the fifth son of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1583|de|1583|ja|1583|zh|1583|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1718]] {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashiro|ja|徳川綱條|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1656|de|1656|ja|1656|zh|1656|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1833]] {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Motoori Ohira|ja|本居大平|12=draft|12=draft}}, a scholar of kokugaku (born {{ill|1756|de|1756|ja|1756|zh|1756|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year, intercalary 9th month ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1843]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hirata Atsutomi|ja|平田篤胤|12=draft|12=draft}}, a kokugakuist (born {{ill|1776|de|1776|ja|1776|zh|1776|12=draft|12=draft}}).
