== Births == * {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛弘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1008]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Ichijō|ja|後一条天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 68th Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1036|de|1036|ja|1036|zh|1036|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Daiji|ja|大治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1127]] {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 77th Emperor (died {{ill|1192|de|1192|ja|1192|zh|1192|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1276]] {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Prince Hisahime|ja|久明親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, who served as the 8th {{ill|Shōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} under the Kamakura shogunate (died {{ill|1328|de|1328|ja|1328|zh|1328|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1544]] {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Takenaka Shigeharu|ja|竹中重治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1579|de|1579|ja|1579|zh|1579|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1709]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kusuki Genkō|ja|朽木玄綱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1770|de|1770|ja|1770|zh|1770|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) with the additional note “秋篠宮妃紀子”.
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenroku|ja|天禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[972]] {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kūya|ja|空也|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the founder of the {{ill|Odori Nenbutsu|ja|踊念仏|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} tradition (born {{ill|903|de|903|ja|903|zh|903|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1585]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tachibana Michiyuki|ja|立花道雪|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165}}, a {{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1513|de|1513|ja|1513|zh|1513|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1603]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Takeda Nobuyoshi|ja|武田信吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the fifth son of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1583|de|1583|ja|1583|zh|1583|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1718]] {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashiro|ja|徳川綱條|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1656|de|1656|ja|1656|zh|1656|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1833]] {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Motoori Ohira|ja|本居大平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a scholar of kokugaku (born {{ill|1756|de|1756|ja|1756|zh|1756|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year, intercalary 9th month ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1843]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hirata Atsutomi|ja|平田篤胤|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a kokugakuist (born {{ill|1776|de|1776|ja|1776|zh|1776|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).
