[[de:September 11 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:September 11 (Lunisolar)]] [[ko:음력 9월 11일]] [[ja:9月11日 (旧暦)]] [[zh:九月十一]] [[en:draft:September 11 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:9月11日 (旧暦)]] [[ar:September 11 (Lunisolar)]]
{{citation needed|September 11 (Lunisolar)}}

{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 11''' is the 11th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō-hōji|ja|天平宝字|qq=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[764]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft}}） – {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro Rebellion|ja|藤原仲麻呂の乱|qq=draft}}. In this uprising, Emperor {{ill|Kōken|ja|孝謙上皇|qq=draft}}’s favorite retainer, {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|qq=draft}}, was targeted by {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro|ja|藤原仲麻呂|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Kōnin|ja|弘仁|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[810]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft}}) – The {{ill|Yakushi no Hen|ja|薬子の変|qq=draft}} occurred. In this incident, {{ill|Fujiwara Yakushi|ja|藤原薬子|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Fujiwara Chūsei|ja|藤原仲成|qq=draft}} (displayed as “仲成”) attempted, unsuccessfully, to restore {{ill|Emperor Heizei|ja|平城天皇|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft}} 3rd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1331]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft}}) – In the {{ill|Genkō Rebellion|ja|元弘の乱|qq=draft}}, when Emperor {{ill|Go-Daigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft}} found himself in dire straits, he summoned {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=draft}}, who then raised an army.
