ill|Takenaka Shigeharu|ja|竹中重治|qq=draft}} (died {{ill|1579|de|1579|ja|1579|zh|1579|qq=draft}}). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1709]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kusuki Genkō|ja|朽木玄綱|qq=draft}} (died {{ill|1770|de|1770|ja|1770|zh|1770|qq=draft}}) with the additional note “秋篠宮妃紀子”.
