[[de:September 11 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:September 11 (Lunisolar)]] [[ko:음력 9월 11일]] [[ja:9月11日 (旧暦)]] [[zh:九月十一]] [[en:draft:September 11 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:9月11日 (旧暦)]] [[ar:September 11 (Lunisolar)]]

{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 11''' is the 11th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō-hōji|ja|天平宝字|qq=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[764]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft}}） – {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro Rebellion|ja|藤原仲麻呂の乱|qq=draft}}. In this uprising, Emperor {{ill|Kōken|ja|孝謙上皇|qq=draft}}’s favorite retainer, {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|qq=draft}}, was targeted by {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro|ja|藤原仲麻呂|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Kōnin|ja|弘仁|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[810]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft}}) – The {{ill|Yakushi no Hen|ja|薬子の変|qq=draft}} occurred. In this incident, {{ill|Fujiwara Yakushi|ja|藤原薬子|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Fujiwara Chūsei|ja|藤原仲成|qq=draft}} (displayed as “仲成”) attempted, unsuccessfully, to restore {{ill|Emperor Heizei|ja|平城天皇|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft}} 3rd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1331]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft}}) – In the {{ill|Genkō Rebellion|ja|元弘の乱|qq=draft}}, when Emperor {{ill|Go-Daigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft}} found himself in dire straits, he summoned {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=draft}}, who then raised an army.
== Births == * {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛弘|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1008]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Ichijō|ja|後一条天皇|qq=draft}}, the 68th Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1036|de|1036|ja|1036|zh|1036|qq=draft}}). * {{ill|Daiji|ja|大治|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1127]] {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河天皇|qq=draft}}, the 77th Emperor (died {{ill|1192|de|1192|ja|1192|zh|1192|qq=draft}}). * {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1276]] {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Prince Hisahime|ja|久明親王|qq=draft}}, who served as the 8th {{ill|Shōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|qq=draft}} under the Kamakura shogunate (died {{ill|1328|de|1328|ja|1328|zh|1328|qq=draft}}). * {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1544]] {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Takenaka Shigeharu|ja|竹中重治|qq=draft}} (died {{ill|1579|de|1579|ja|1579|zh|1579|qq=draft}}). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1709]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kusuki Genkō|ja|朽木玄綱|qq=draft}} (died {{ill|1770|de|1770|ja|1770|zh|1770|qq=draft}}) with the additional note “秋篠宮妃紀子”.
