{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月十一|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 11일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 11''' is the 11th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō-hōji|ja|天平宝字|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[764]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=}}） – {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro Rebellion|ja|藤原仲麻呂の乱|qq=draft|qq=}}. In this uprising, Emperor {{ill|Kōken|ja|孝謙上皇|qq=draft|qq=}}’s favorite retainer, {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|qq=draft|qq=}}, was targeted by {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro|ja|藤原仲麻呂|qq=draft|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kōnin|ja|弘仁|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[810]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Yakushi no Hen|ja|薬子の変|qq=draft|qq=}} occurred. In this incident, {{ill|Fujiwara Yakushi|ja|藤原薬子|qq=draft|qq=}} and {{ill|Fujiwara Chūsei|ja|藤原仲成|qq=draft|qq=}} (displayed as “仲成”) attempted, unsuccessfully, to restore {{ill|Emperor Heizei|ja|平城天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}. * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1331]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – In the {{ill|Genkō Rebellion|ja|元弘の乱|qq=draft|qq=}}, when Emperor {{ill|Go-Daigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=}} found himself in dire straits, he summoned {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=draft|qq=}}, who then raised an army.
== Births == * {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛弘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1008]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Ichijō|ja|後一条天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 68th Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1036|de|1036|ja|1036|zh|1036|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Daiji|ja|大治|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1127]] {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 77th Emperor (died {{ill|1192|de|1192|ja|1192|zh|1192|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1276]] {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Prince Hisahime|ja|久明親王|qq=draft|qq=}}, who served as the 8th {{ill|Shōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|qq=draft|qq=}} under the Kamakura shogunate (died {{ill|1328|de|1328|ja|1328|zh|1328|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juli