{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月十一|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 11일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 11''' is the 11th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō-hōji|ja|天平宝字|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[764]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=}}） – {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro Rebellion|ja|藤原仲麻呂の乱|qq=draft|qq=}}. In this uprising, Emperor {{ill|Kōken|ja|孝謙上皇|qq=draft|qq=}}’s favorite retainer, {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|qq=draft|qq=}}, was targeted by {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro|ja|藤原仲麻呂|qq=draft|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kōnin|ja|弘仁|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[810]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Yakushi no Hen|ja|薬子の変|qq=draft|qq=}} occurred. In this incident, {{ill|Fujiwara Yakushi|ja|藤原薬子|qq=draft|qq=}} and {{ill|Fujiwara Chūsei|ja|藤原仲成|qq=draft|qq=}} (displayed as “仲成”) attempted, unsuccessfully, to restore {{ill|Emperor Heizei|ja|平城天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}. * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1331]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – In the {{ill|Genkō Rebellion|ja|元弘の乱|qq=draft|qq=}}, when Emperor {{ill|Go-Daigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=}} found himself in dire straits, he summoned {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=draft|qq=}}, who then raised an army.
== Births == * {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛弘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1008]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Ichijō|ja|後一条天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 68th Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1036|de|1036|ja|1036|zh|1036|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Daiji|ja|大治|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1127]] {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 77th Emperor (died {{ill|1192|de|1192|ja|1192|zh|1192|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1276]] {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Prince Hisahime|ja|久明親王|qq=draft|qq=}}, who served as the 8th {{ill|Shōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|qq=draft|qq=}} under the Kamakura shogunate (died {{ill|1328|de|1328|ja|1328|zh|1328|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1544]] {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Takenaka Shigeharu|ja|竹中重治|qq=draft|qq=}} (died {{ill|1579|de|1579|ja|1579|zh|1579|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1709]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kusuki Genkō|ja|朽木玄綱|qq=draft|qq=}} (died {{ill|1770|de|1770|ja|1770|zh|1770|qq=draft|qq=}}) with the additional note “秋篠宮妃紀子”.
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenroku|ja|天禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[972]] {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kūya|ja|空也|qq=draft|qq=}}, the founder of the {{ill|Odori Nenbutsu|ja|踊念仏|qq=draft|qq=}} tradition (born {{ill|903|de|903|ja|903|zh|903|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1585]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tachibana Michiyuki|ja|立花道雪|qq=draft|qq=}} {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165|qq=}}, a {{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (born {{ill|1513|de|1513|ja|1513|zh|1513|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1603]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Takeda Nobuyoshi|ja|武田信吉|qq=draft|qq=}}, the fifth son of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=draft|qq=}} (born {{ill|1583|de|1583|ja|1583|zh|1583|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1718]] {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashiro|ja|徳川綱條|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 3rd head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩|qq=draft|qq=}} (born {{ill|1656|de|1656|ja|1656|zh|1656|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1833]] {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Motoori Ohira|ja|本居大平|qq=draft|qq=}}, a scholar of kokugaku (born {{ill|1756|de|1756|ja|1756|zh|1756|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 14th year, intercalary 9th month ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1843]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hirata Atsutomi|ja|平田篤胤|qq=draft|qq=}}, a kokugakuist (born {{ill|1776|de|1776|ja|1776|zh|1776|qq=draft|qq=}}).
