== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō-hōji|1=Tenpyō-hōji|2=ja|3=天平宝字|ja|天平宝字|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpyō-hōji|qq=}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[764]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 10|qq=}}） – {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro Rebellion|ja|藤原仲麻呂の乱|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara Nakamaro Rebellion|qq=}}. In this uprising, Emperor {{ill|Kōken|ja|孝謙上皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōken|qq=}}’s favorite retainer, {{ill|Dōkyō|ja|道鏡|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dōkyō|qq=}}, was targeted by {{ill|Fujiwara Nakamaro|ja|藤原仲麻呂|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara Nakamaro|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kōnin|ja|弘仁|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōnin|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[810]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 12|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Yakushi no Hen|ja|薬子の変|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yakushi no Hen|qq=}} occurred. In this incident, {{ill|Fujiwara Yakushi|ja|藤原薬子|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara Yakushi|qq=}} and {{ill|Fujiwara Chūsei|ja|藤原仲成|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara Chūsei|qq=}} (displayed as “仲成”) attempted, unsuccessfully, to restore {{ill|Emperor Heizei|ja|平城天皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Heizei|qq=}}. * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gentoku|qq=}} 3rd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1331]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 13|qq=}}) – In the {{ill|Genkō Rebellion|ja|元弘の乱|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō Rebellion|qq=}}, when Emperor {{ill|Go-Daigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Daigo|qq=}} found himself in dire straits, he summoned {{ill|Kusunoki Masashige|ja|楠木正成|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusunoki Masashige|qq=}}, who then raised an army.
== Births == * {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛弘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kankō|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1008]] {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 12|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Ichijō|ja|後一条天皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Ichijō|qq=}}, the 68th Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1036|de|1036|ja|1036|zh|1036|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1036|qq=}}). * {{ill|Daiji|ja|大治|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daiji|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1127]] {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 18|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河天皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=}}, the 77th Emperor (died {{ill|1192|de|1192|ja|1192|zh|1192|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1192|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenji|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1276]] {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Prince Hisahime|ja|久明親王|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Hisahime|qq=}}, who served as the 8th {{ill|Shōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōgun|qq=}} under the Kamakura shogunate (died {{ill|1328|de|1328|ja|1328|zh|1328|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1328|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1544]] {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September 27|qq=}}) – {{ill|Takenaka Shigeharu|ja|竹中重治|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takenaka Shigeharu|qq=}} (died {{ill|1579|de|1579|ja|1579|zh|1579|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1579|qq=}}). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1709]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 13|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kusuki Genkō|ja|朽木玄綱|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusuki Genkō|qq=}} (died {{ill|1770|de|1770|ja|1770|zh|1770|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1770|qq=}}) with the additional note “秋篠宮妃紀子”.
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenroku|ja|天禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenroku|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[972]] {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 20|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kūya|ja|空也|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kūya|qq=}}, the founder of the {{ill|Odori Nenbutsu|ja|踊念仏|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Odori Nenbutsu|qq=}} tradition (born {{ill|903|de|903|ja|903|zh|903|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/903|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1585]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tachibana Michiyuki|ja|立花道雪|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana Michiyuki|qq=}} {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165|qq=}}, a {{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Busho (Rank)|qq=}} (born {{ill|1513|de|1513|ja|1513|zh|1513|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1513|qq=}}). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1603]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 15|qq=}}) – {{ill|Takeda Nobuyoshi|ja|武田信吉|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Nobuyoshi|qq=}}, the fifth son of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} (born {{ill|1583|de|1583|ja|1583|zh|1583|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1583|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1718]] {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 4|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashiro|ja|徳川綱條|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Tsunashiro|qq=}}, the 3rd head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mito Domain|qq=}} (born {{ill|1656|de|1656|ja|1656|zh|1656|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1656|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1833]] {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}}) – {{ill|Motoori Ohira|ja|本居大平|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Motoori Ohira|qq=}}, a scholar of kokugaku (born {{ill|1756|de|1756|ja|1756|zh|1756|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1756|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 14th year, intercalary 9th month ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1843]] {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hirata Atsutomi|ja|平田篤胤|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirata Atsutomi|qq=}}, a kokugakuist (born {{ill|1776|de|1776|ja|1776|zh|1776|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1776|qq=}}).
