== Deaths == * [[:en:Tenroku|Tenroku]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[972]] [[:en:October 20|October 20]]) – [[:en:Kūya|Kūya]], the founder of the {{ill|Odori Nenbutsu|ja|踊念仏|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Odori Nenbutsu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 念仏}} tradition (born [[:en:903|903]]). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 13rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1585|1585]] [[:en:November 2|November 2]]) – [[:en:Tachibana Dōsetsu|Tachibana Michiyuki]] {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165|qq=}}, a {{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Busho (Rank)|qq=}} (born [[:en:1513|1513]]). * [[:en:Keichō|Keichō]] 8th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1603|1603]] [[:en:October 15|October 15]]) – [[:en:Takeda Nobuyoshi|Takeda Nobuyoshi]], the fifth son of [[:en:Tokugawa Ieyasu|Tokugawa Ieyasu]] (born [[:en:1583|1583]]). * [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1718|1718]] [[:en:October 4|October 4]]) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashiro|ja|徳川綱條|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Tsunashiro|qq=}}, the 3rd head of the [[:en:Mito Domain|Mito Domain]] (born [[:en:1656|1656]]). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1833|1833]] [[:en:October 23|October 23]]) – [[:en:Motoori Ōhira|Motoori Ohira]], a scholar of kokugaku (born [[:en:1756|1756]]). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 14th year, intercalary 9th month ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1843|1843]] [[:en:November 2|November 2]]) – [[:en:Hirata Atsutane|Hirata Atsutomi]], a kokugakuist (born [[:en:1776|1776]]).
